				<outline text="I updated the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/scripting/outlineBrowser2&quot;&gt;outlinerBrowser&lt;/a&gt; code, which is used in various places. I've seen other devs using it, which is good. It now supports &lt;i&gt;image&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;inlineImage&lt;/i&gt; attributes, as they are used in &quot;Old School&quot;.  " created="Sun, 24 Jul 2022 15:15:50 GMT" type="outline"/>
