					<outline text="PS: See the previous &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/2022/07/19/152235.html?title=devNotesForMarkdownInRss&quot;&gt;two&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/2022/07/18/163658.html?title=twitterRssMarkdown&quot;&gt;day's&lt;/a&gt; posts about Markdown in RSS feeds.  " created="Wed, 20 Jul 2022 18:55:30 GMT"/>
