					<outline text="I lost points for &quot;unsafe following,&quot; something I abhor, but I guess I must &lt;i&gt;occasionally&lt;/i&gt; actually do, lesson learned, I'll try to do better. " created="Wed, 06 Jul 2022 23:28:55 GMT"/>
					<outline text="But I contest the hit for &quot;hard braking.&quot; I know &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/2022/05/14.html#a142227&quot;&gt;exactly when that I happened&lt;/a&gt;. I had driven to &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phoenicia,_New_York&quot;&gt;Phoenicia&lt;/a&gt; to pick up a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yelp.com/biz/brios-pizzeria-and-restaurant-phoenicia&quot;&gt;pizza&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=&quot;http://brios.net/&quot;&gt;Brio's&lt;/a&gt; and on the drive home, I had to hit the brakes, hard -- to avoid killing a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/search?q=wild+turkey+on+the+road&quot;&gt;wild turkey&lt;/a&gt; who was slowly making its way across the highway. The pizza went flying, along with a fair amount of sauce and cheese, soiling the carpet in front of the passenger seat on my almost new Model Y, which is scary for a new car, for fear it'll &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/2020/08/30/152537.html?title=howToFightMiceInCars&quot;&gt;attract rodents&lt;/a&gt;. " created="Wed, 06 Jul 2022 23:32:33 GMT"/>
					<outline text="But I digress. I hit the brakes to save the turkey. And now I learn because of that fukcing turkey, no &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.teslarati.com/tesla-fsd-beta-1-million-drivers/&quot;&gt;Full Self Driving beta&lt;/a&gt; for Uncle Davey. Oy. Fuckin turkeys, they'll get you every time. " created="Wed, 06 Jul 2022 23:33:03 GMT"/>
