					<outline text="Another post that came straight from a &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/davewiner/status/1543959036571312128&quot;&gt;twitter thread&lt;/a&gt;." created="Mon, 04 Jul 2022 15:19:00 GMT"/>
